{"tid":572029,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰鬥民族adore] 國際奧委會決定俄羅斯選手冬奧閉幕禮不能持國旗","createTime":"2018-02-25T08:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T08:38:46.000Z","uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a26002122cb6352e218456997ea6878088d1430","tid":572029,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382472-20180225.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382472-20180225.htm&d=nwB2E2dYtjwmbrruhglyTpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=e53f4f70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382472-20180225.htm&h=7be2ebdb\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382472-20180225.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n國際奧委會決定，來自俄羅斯的選手在平昌冬奧閉幕式上，不能持俄羅斯國旗進場。<br />\n<br />\n這項決定獲國際奧委會成員一致通過。<br />\n<br />\n不過，消息透露，奧委會同時認為，只要平昌冬奧再沒有涉及俄羅斯運動員的禁藥測試呈陽性，俄羅斯幾天或幾星期內可重獲國際賽資格。<br />\n<br />\n現時有兩名來自俄羅斯的平昌冬奧運動員，藥檢呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯由於在索契冬奧被揭涉及政府層級用藥，因而遭國際奧委會禁止參加平昌冬奧，但合資格的個別運動員可以「來自俄羅斯的奧林匹克運動員」名義參賽。"},{"pid":"c7629b67ccb26637012a44f51ab018059e9f01ca","tid":572029,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯人浸冰水.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯人玩火.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n普京大帝騎熊.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n普京大帝玩柔道.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82008587b1fa598a23238b8d29b8b6e7b34adb89","tid":572029,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯人/普京大帝柯個屎都話係戰鬥民族真男人嘅垃圾黃蛾點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8ff2037897e86671ba3b9b000e258f0a5c0e40","tid":572029,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}